The paper discusses wireless communication strategies for IoT applications, which falls under the category of networked systems and communication (cs.NI). The paper also presents new energy efficiency performance limits, which involves information theory (cs.IT) and control systems (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper discusses the design guidelines for green transmission, which involves cyber-physical systems (cs.CY) and multimedia (cs.MM) since IoT applications often involve multimedia data.
